trans-unit.source: Determines which date to include in the names of the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener"></xref> class log files.
trans-unit.target: Anger vilket datum som ska ingå i namnen på de <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener"> </xref> klassen loggfiler.

trans-unit.source: Assign one of the LogFileCreationScheduleOption enumeration values to the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A> property to specify which date to include in the names of its log files.
trans-unit.target: Tilldela en LogFileCreationScheduleOption uppräkningsvärdena till den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>att ange vilket datum som ska ingå i namnen på loggfilerna.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.LogFileCreationSchedule%2A>

trans-unit.source: Include the current date in the log file name.
trans-unit.target: Med det aktuella datumet i loggfilens namn.

trans-unit.source: Do not include the date in the log file name.
trans-unit.target: Inkludera inte datumet i loggfilens namn.

trans-unit.source: Include the first day of the current week in the log file name.
trans-unit.target: Inkludera den första dagen i den aktuella veckan i loggfilens namn.
